parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Rusted brake lines can cause brake failure, leading to increased stopping distances and accidents.
symptoms: Brake pedal goes to the floor
large cloud of smoke comes out of the engine compartment
brake fluid hits the hot exhaust manifold.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning ABS can cause the vehicle to not stop properly, leading to accidents or near-misses, especially in tight areas or around children.
symptoms: Anti-lock brakes pulsate at low speed on dry pavement
arbitrary activation of the ABS brakes at slow speeds or when parking
vehicle continues moving for a few inches to a few feet.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield wiper motor can reduce visibility during rain or snow, increasing the risk of accidents.

requiring repeated attempts to activate
or may not work at all

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic rearview mirror controller can reduce visibility, making it difficult to change lanes or park, increasing the risk of accidents.
